    <item>
      <title>美国反垄断审判开始，谷歌广告帝国遭遇抨击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/google-s-ad-empire-under-fire-with-us-antitrust-trial-to-begin</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Alphabet Inc. 旗下谷歌周一再次回到法庭，面对美国司法部的指控，指控其操纵价值 6770 亿美元的展示广告市场，违反了反垄断法。就在一个月前，谷歌刚刚输掉了一项具有里程碑意义的裁决，裁定其非法主导在线搜索市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/google-s-ad-empire-under-fire-with-us-antitrust-trial-to-begin</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
